54
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,760
Gu Jingshi,

55
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,890
I like you.

56
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:37,260
Confessions

57
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,920
