94
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,080
Family?

95
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:06,990
Jingshi.

96
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,260
Are you really going to be so ruthless?

97
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,810
Actions have consequences.

98
00:08:10,810 --> 00:08:12,340
