106
00:08:38,690 --> 00:08:40,090
Miss Jian, could you please...

107
00:08:40,090 --> 00:08:40,890
No.

108
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,840
I cannot forgive him.

109
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:43,679
