139
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,060
Really?

140
00:10:44,090 --> 00:10:45,800
Go squeeze a bowl of lemon juice for me.

141
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:46,850
Lemon juice?

142
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,440
Okay.

143
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:57,040
Lemon juice.

144
