149
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:43,020
Wow, that's amazing!

150
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,840
Gu Jingshi, you're incredible!

151
00:11:46,190 --> 00:11:47,290
However, due to its age,

152
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:48,690
